edu.uidaho.junicon.runtime.junicon.annotations

Annotation Type MParameter


  • @Target(value=METHOD)
 @Repeatable(value=MParameters.class)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface MParameter
    Annotation interface for method parameters. Bound to the actual method, not the field holding the exposed method reference.

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      String name
      Original name of declared parameter.
      String reifiedName
      Only the reified parameter exists, which holds the value.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      String defaultValue
      Default value for parameter, or null if no default or is empty.
      boolean isVararg
      Is variable argument.
      String type
      Declared type.

    • Element Detail
